04/05/2003
TASHKENT, Uzbekistan -- At the EBRD annual meeting in Tashkent on Saturday (3 May), EBRD President Jean Lemierre said Croatia has achieved excellent economic results in the past several years. 
Croatian Finance Minister Mato Crkvenac met with Lemierre to discuss new joint projects for job creation, infrastructure and environmental protection. 
Lemierre reportedly accepted an invitation to visit Croatia in September. 
(Vjesnik, HINA, BBC - 03/05/03)
